Preparation
+++++++++++

1. To create the 'contain' binary:

$ gcc -o contain contain.c -lrt

2. Change ownership of the binary to 'root.root' and move to /usr/local/bin:

$ sudo chown root.root ./contain
$ sudo mv ./contain /usr/local/bin

3. An up to date rootfs can be retrieved from the following URL:

https://partner-images.canonical.com/core/bionic/current
